---
title: Apple Skillet 'Pan Cake' Serves 2 | with Cherry Spread
description: Mastering the art of skillet cakes is easier than you think! Tonight's one-pan wonder is studded with sweet apple and topped with tart cherry spread! You won't believe how easy this dessert comes together!
